{"type": "article", "id": 28779, "title": "老房子里改造出来的青旅，这家看起来格外明净", "description": "这种位于城中心且有当地特色的老建筑是改造青旅的最好选择。", "date": "2016-06-28T06:54:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3253, "name": "葡萄牙"}, {"id": 29474, "name": "Conii Hostel"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 183, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703150451KkJU0A8SEyQ3d4ab.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>葡萄牙最南端的阿尔加维是欧洲人最爱去的度假胜地之一，有大量的历史建筑风格各异的旅馆，人们的生活悠闲，喜欢吃海鲜喝葡萄酒，常年源源不断的游客使得这里老房子常常被改建成旅馆。我们曾经介绍过一幢将祖父的房子改建成只有 9 间房的旅馆，这种接近家庭民宿的方式让旅馆保留了当地的特色。</p>\n<p>夸尔泰拉（Quarteira）上的 <a href=\"http://www.coniihostel.com/en/\">Conii Hostel </a>原本也是一个建于 1896 年的老房子，一直被同一户家庭使用，在 1970 年代之后就向游客提供住宿。随着城市的变化和建筑层高的加高，这种只有两层楼的方形建筑变成了旧时代建筑的代表，它的四面墙体是独立的，两面临街，处于街道的转角，另外两面则挨着小花园，白色的墙面尽管有斑驳的痕迹，倒也显得古朴典雅。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150432D70vWRS6quQPK9mA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">改造前</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>这种位于城中心且有当地特色的老建筑是改造青旅的最好选择，而为了增加更多房间，建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://www.estudiods.com/hostel_conii.html\">ODS</a> 决定加建一层。他们使用深灰色的钢材做结构和主体，看起来非常现代，与砖墙建筑产生黑白色和材料的对比。窗户的宽窄和排列位置却是一致的，远看像是增加了一道边。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150433fLhWcS6YQE8e2vyD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150433NPXLCZfQSd3uJleO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031504343oMIsLHEpnzdGUYl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150435o69wCM0zDfUAcdrN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>室内原本有一条走廊将酒店切成两半，楼梯也在走廊上，新建时只保留了楼梯的一部分，在垂直方向划出了另一条走廊，所有房间都沿着方形的布局和走廊的切割方式显得非常规整。</p>\n<p class=\"\">室内只使用了蓝、白、黑和浅黄色这几种颜色，地板是 10 ×10 厘米的方形花砖，非常清新。其中柜台等家具使用了定向刨花板（OSB 板），是一种在欧洲流行的合成木板。<br></p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150436J7erwpYuOU3j214S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150436pg9HaLEtk2TrI7DS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>一楼由 4 个同样大小的休闲区组成，包括接待处、带开放式的厨房的餐厅、酒吧和客厅。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150437D1P37mcBGv6JUSzq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150437X1IgUoMdzAN8KxyH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031504389HA3e6z571IpbBZu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150438tZWw4SbNkmKXM5Uy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150439YQENIOrtJo8uKZTD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031504407NljsHV15G8aQBA9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150440P6nj2QbmCYs5aq7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p>二楼分布有 6 间床位房，一共可住 36 个人。这里的床位更像盒子，用黑色窗帘做遮挡。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031504414yh3OLXK8ZPbjqzC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031504412OSl8LtiIfNkWYZJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150442pntsNxrf0ihEwRVL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150442fCVunvY8M03DTNqQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150443zCrf9bNOyUD2eAm4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150444HdjGqB8oAKI9hQzr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150445o891VfLxbEzFamBC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150445RuDa8vOke6j3NCwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>三楼的 9 个房间都带有独立卫浴，其中两个房间也是可住 4 人的床位房。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150446AVXjufFUsxw9HJdD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150447rhkom2FLpRsDBbaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150448SgLcH7Dha4l6CmJq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031504481ul7d36VySPCG8Rf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150450AwSmhoXnHEuMirzx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703150450c8PEJmy5KxD2TrWf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/789909/hostel-conii-estudio-ods\">archdaily</a>、<a href=\"http://www.coniihostel.com/en/\">coniihostel</a></p>\n\n"}